    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, combine your<strong> red chilli relish</strong>, <strong>chipotle paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> in a bowl – this is your <strong>sweet chilli sauce</strong></p>",
