    {
      "instruction": "<p>Pat your <strong>hake fillet[s]</strong> dry with kitchen<strong> </strong>paper and add them to a <strong>tin foil</strong>-lined baking tray (or two!)</p><p>Season the hake with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and spread the <strong>sweet chilli sauce</strong> over evenly</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 12-15 min or until the fish is cooked through – this is your <strong>sweet chilli hake</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1700043873868-x200.jpg",
