        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the hake is in the oven, peel and finely slice (don't chop!) your<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>pak choi</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and cut in half, separating the <strong>white bases</strong> and<strong> green tops</strong></p><p>Boil half a kettle</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1700043874467-x200.jpg",
