    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>sweet chilli hake</strong> over the <strong>ginger rice </strong>with the<strong> sesame pak choi</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
